
ḳhuub hai shauq kā ye pahlū bhī 
maiñ bhī barbād ho gayā tū bhī 
husn-e-maġhmūm tamkanat meñ tirī 
farq aayā na yak-sar-e-mū bhī 
ye na sochā thā zer-e-sāya-e-zulf 
ki bichhaḌ jā.egī ye ḳhush-bū bhī 
husn kahtā thā chheḌne vaale 
chheḌnā hī to bas nahīñ chhū bhī 
haa.e vo us kā mauj-ḳhez badan 
maiñ to pyāsā rahā lab-e-jū bhī 
yaad aate haiñ mo.ajize apne 
aur us ke badan kā jaadū bhī 
yāsmīñ us kī ḳhaas mahram-e-rāz 
yaad aayā karegī ab tū bhī 
yaad se us kī hai mirā parhez 
ai sabā ab na aa.iyo tū bhī 
haiñ yahī 'jaun-elia' jo kabhī 
saḳht maġhrūr bhī the bad-ḳhū bhī 